<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4918883>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 298–306. Primary type specimens and labels of New Zealand Zopheridae: Synchitini. 298) Holotype labels, Pristoderus tuberculatus (Broun, 1880; as Ulonotus); 299–300) Lectotype, Pristoderus undosus (Broun, 1882; as Dryptops); labels; 301–302) Holotype, Pristoderus uropterus (Broun, 1912; as Ulonotus); labels; 303–305) Lectotype, Pristoderus viridipictus (Wollaston, 1873; as Tarphiomimetes); card-mount; labels; 306) Lectotype, Pristoderus wakefieldi (Sharp, 1877; as Enarsus)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4918883/files/figure.png" .

